cloud-init (0.6.3-0ubuntu2) quantal; urgency=high

  * Added -generic to Xen kernels list since -virtual has been dropped with
    Quantal. (LP: #1005551)

 -- Ben Howard <ben.howard@ubuntu.com>  Tue, 29 May 2012 12:59:01 -0600

